1.title: Cobbster vs JTE
1.plot: Finally, Cobbster and JTE went head to head in a movie trivia game and the mispronunciation heard around the world happened when JTE was asked about Jurassic Park. Enjoy.

2.title: Katee Sackhoff vs. Ken Napzok (Round 1 Ultimate Schmoedown)
2.plot: The Tournament begins. Ken Napzok and Katee Sackhoff went at it in the first round of the tournament of champions, The Ultimate Schmoedown movie trivia contest.

3.title: Mark Reilly vs Alicia Malone
3.plot: The tournament continues. Mark "Yodi" Reilly and Alicia "Bugsy" Malone go head to head in the second match of THE ULTIMATE SCHMOEDOWN.

4.title: Bonnie Somerville Vs Josh Macuga
4.plot: This week; two of the biggest personalities to hit the Schmoeville airwaves go head to head in a tight battle. Bonnie Somerville squares off against Josh "The Wildman" Macuga.

5.title: Mark Ellis Vs Cobbster
5.plot: Mark Ellis came in a heavy favorite against the intern, Cobbster. Did he destroy the kid from California or was it an unexpected nail biter?

6.title: Navid McIlhargey vs Grae Drake
6.plot: We have reached the 5th match of tournament. The stage is set...Producer Navid Mcilhargey takes on Rotten Tomatoes senior editor Grae Drake in a battle for the ages.

7.title: Tiffany Smith Vs Finstock
7.plot: In the 6th match of the first round, we have one of the biggest rivalries in Schmoeville history. Our esteemed co-host Tiffany Smith goes up against Schmoeville's resident madman Finstock.

8.title: The Kid Vs JTE
8.plot: In the 7th match of the first round, It was another nail biter in the Ultimate Schmoedown Movie Trivia. This battle saw the artist formerly known as JTI, now known as JTE battle our intern The Kid.

9.title: Cody vs Kristian Harloff
9.plot: The Ultimate Schmoedown Trivia Contest continues!. The final match of round 1. It is Harloff vs the new intern Cody aka Upham.

10.title: Grae Drake Vs Mark Reilly
10.plot: It is the FIRST battle in ROUND 2 of The Ultimate Schmoedown and it pitted fan favorite Grae Drake against tournament favorite Mark "Yodi" Reilly. See who prevailed.

11.title: Mark Ellis Vs JTE
11.plot: It is the 2nd match in the 2nd round of the Ultimate Schmoedown. Mark Ellis battles JTE. It is a battle you DONT want to miss.

12.title: The Trial of JTE
12.plot: If you have been watching the Ultimate Schmoedown, you may or may not know that JTE was accused of cheating. He was put on trial and this is what happened.

13.title: Kristian Harloff Vs Finstock
13.plot: In a round 2 match up, the Diabolical Finstock goes up against Darth Harloff in an epic battle.

14.title: Josh Macuga Vs Ken Napzok
14.plot: It is a battle between Ken Napzok and Josh Macuga in the Ultimate Schmoedown.

15.title: Mark Reilly Vs JTE
15.plot: In the first Final Four match-up, JTE tries to continue his Cinderella streak against the mighty Yodi, Mark Reilly.

16.title: Kristian Harloff Vs Josh Macuga
16.plot: The last match before the finals. Kristian Harloff faces off against Josh Macuga. There was controversy.

17.title: Mark Reilly Vs Josh Macuga
17.plot: The Finals of the Ultimate Schmoedown between Josh Macuga and Mark Reilly.

1.title: Jedi Vs Newbie
1.plot: Match 1 of Round 1 of 2015 Ultimate Schmoedown happened last night. Team Jedi (Mike Black + Ken Napzok) went up against Team Newbie (Sasha Perl Raver + Miri Jedekin.

2.title: Machinima Vs Profiles
2.plot: Match 2 of Round 1 of 2015 Ultimate Schmoedown happened last night. Team Machinima (Elliot + Ricky) went up against Team Profiles (Alicia Malone + Scott Mantz.

3.title: Geek Vs B.O.B.
3.plot: Match 4 of Round 1 of 2015 Ultimate Schmoedown was a battle between the monster Screen Junkies (HAL RUDNICK + NICK MUNDY) against the virtually unknown Top 10 team (MATT KNOST + JOHN ROCHA).

4.title: Top 10 Vs Screen Junkies
4.plot: Match 4 of Round 1 of 2015 Ultimate Schmoedown was a battle between the monster Screen Junkies (HAL RUDNICK + NICK MUNDY) against the virtually unknown Top 10 team (MATT KNOST + JOHN ROCHA).

5.title: Collider Vs SourceFed
5.plot: Latest match in The Ultimate Schmoedown 2015. Team Collider (Dennis Tzeng + Jon Schnepp) squared off against Team Sourcefed (Stever Zaragoza and Matt Lieberman).

6.title: B-Team Vs Champs
6.plot: Match 6 of Round 1 of 2015 Ultimate Schmoedown was a battle between the lovable but possibly outmatched BTeam (Cobbster, Ace and Upham) going against one of the faves to win the whole thing, Team Champs (Current Schmoedown singles champ Mark Reilly and Screenjunkies MovieFights champ Dan Murrell).

7.title: GMP Vs Rotten Tomatoes
7.plot: It was match 7 of round 1 of the Schmoedown. Team GMP (Josh Macuga and Ben Begley vs Team Rotten Tomatoes (Grae Drake and Matt Atchity).

8.title: Nerdist Vs Schmoes
8.plot: It was match 8 of round 1 of the Schmoedown. Team NERDIST (Jessica Chobot + Dan Casey) vs Team SCHMOES (Kristian Harloff + Mark Ellis).

9.title: Top 10 Vs Champs
9.plot: It was match 1 of round 2 of the Schmoedown. Team CHAMPS (Mark Reilly+ Dan Murrell) vs Team TOP 10 (John Rocha + Matt Knost).

10.title: Schmoes Vs Newbie
10.plot: It was match 2 of round 2 of the Schmoedown. Team NEWBIES (Sasha Perl Raver + Miri Jedekin) vs Team SCHMOES (Kristian Harloff + Mark Ellis).

11.title: Machinima Vs Rotten Tomatoes
11.plot: It was match 3 of round 2 of the Schmoedown. Team Machinima (Ricky Hayberg + Elliot Dewberry) vs Team Rotten Tomatoes (Matt Achity + Grae Drake).

12.title: B.O.B. Vs Collider
12.plot: Its Box Office Breakdown against Dennis and Schnepp in the final match of the second round. The winner plays Top 10 team in the Semi finals.

13.title: B.O.B. Vs Top 10
13.plot: Its the Rocky of the tourney Box Office Breakdown against Rocha and Knost in the first match of semi-finals. The winner goes to the finals.

14.title: Rotten Tomatoes Vs Schmoes
14.plot: The semi-finals!. SCHMOES VS ROTTEN TOMATOES. Who will play Team BOB in the finals?

1.title: John Campea Vs Dan Murrell
1.plot: It's the Movie Trivia Schmoedown with a Round 1 match-up for the ages. John 'La Cosa Nostra' Campea takes on Dangerous Dan Murrell from Screen Junkies. Who will win? Who will take one step closer to the championship?

2.title: John Rocha Vs Scott Mantz
2.plot: It's the Movie Trivia Schmoedown with a Round 2 match-up that will live in infamy. "The Outlaw" John Rocha takes on the Mantz-Man Scott Mantz from Access Hollywood. Who will win? Who will take one step closer to the championship?

3.title: Samm Levine Vs Hal Rudnick
3.plot: It's another action-trivia packed Movie Trivia Schmoedown with a match-up between two behemoths of knowledge. Hal Rudnick from Screen Junkies takes on the 'Inglorious One,' Samm Levine from 'Freaks and Geeks' and 'Inglorious Basterds!' Who will win this time? And who will take that crucial first step towards the championship.

4.title: Josh Macuga Vs Clarke Wolfe
4.plot: It's another action-trivia packed Movie Trivia Schmoedown with a match-up between two competitors worth their weight in movie knowledge. "Classy Clarke Wolfe" takes on the "The Wildman," Josh Macuga. Who will win this time? And who will be one step closer to the championship?

5.title: Jon Schnepp Vs Finstock
5.plot: It's that time - The Movie Trivia Schmoedown to end all Movie Trivia Schmoedowns - Big Jon Schnepp takes on the enigma that is Finstock. Who will win this time? And who will take a step closer to challenging the champion for the #Schmoedown belt?

7.title: Team Schmoes Vs Team B.O.B. (Championship Match)
7.plot: It's the TEAM TITLE MATCH on the Movie Trivia Schmoedown. Box Office Breakdown goes against the might of Team Schmoes to decide the first, ever winner of the Team Championship Schmoedown. Who wins?

8.title: Umberto Gonzalez Vs Jeff Sneider
8.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, The Wrap's film reporter Jeff Sneider takes on the scoop-master Umberto "El Mayimbe" Gonzales from Heroic Hollywood. Who will win this time? Can one of these guys challenge Reilly for the #Schmoedown belt?

9.title: Dan Murrell Vs Scott Mantz
9.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown with an epic match with title implications. "Dangerous" Dan Murrell takes on Scott "Movie" Mantz with the winner able to take on Mark "Yodi" Reilly for the Schmoedown Title. Who will win?

10.title: Clarke Wolfe Vs Finstock
10.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown with an epic match with title implications. "Classy" Clarke Wolfe takes on the enigma that is Finstock. The winner will take one step closer to the title of Schmoedown Champion. Who will win?

11.title: John Rocha Vs Josh Macuga
11.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown with an all new epic match. "The Wildman" Josh Macuga takes on "The Outlaw" John Rocha. The winner will take one step closer to the title of Schmoedown Champion. Who will win?

12.title: Kristian Harloff Vs Andy Signore
12.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown with an all new epic match. Kristian "Darth" Harloff takes on "The Judge" Andy Serkis. The winner will take one step closer to the title of Schmoedown Champion. Who will win?

13.title: Grae Drake Vs Jason Inman
13.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, Rotten Tomatoes own Grae Drake takes on DC All Access's Jason Inman in a barn-burner of a movie trivia contest. Who will win and take that step closer for a chance at winning the championship belt?

14.title: Samm Levine Vs Jeff Sneider
14.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, Jeff Sneider takes on "The Inglorious One" Samm Levine. Who will win and take that one step closer for a chance at winning the championship belt?

15.title: Mark Ellis Vs JTE
15.plot: It's the big one. The one for all the glory. It's the Movie Trivia Schmoedown with a HUGE match of two mega powers: Mark "Yodi" Reilly defends his belt against 'Dangerous' Dan Murrell. Who will win and take that championship belt?

16.title: Championship: Reilly Vs Murrell
16.plot: It's the big one. The one for all the glory. It's the Movie Trivia Schmoedown with a HUGE match of two mega powers: Mark "Yodi" Reilly defends his belt against 'Dangerous' Dan Murrell. Who will win and take that championship belt?

17.title: Matt Knost Vs Eliot Dewberry
17.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, it's Collider's own Matt Knost from The Top Ten show going up against Eliot Dewberry from ETC. Who will win and take that step closer for a chance at winning the championship belt?

18.title: Jon Schnepp Vs Khail Anonymous
18.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, it's Collider's own Big Jon Schnepp taking on Khail Anonymous. Who will win and take that step closer for a chance at winning the championship belt?

19.title: Clarke Wolfe Vs Samm Levine
19.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week is a HUGE match with the number 2 contender 'Classy' Clarke Wolfe' taking on the number 3 contender, 'The Inglorious One,' Samm Levine. Winner get's a chance to take on Dan Murrell for the championship belt.

20.title: Kristian Harloff Vs Jason Inman
20.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, a HUGE match is going down with Inman v Harloff Dawn of Schmoeville. That's right, it's Collider's own Kristian Harloff taking on DC All Access' Jason Inman - winner will enter the Ultimate Schmoedown Tournament for a chance to run the table and take a shot at the belt.

21.title: Scott Mantz Vs John Rocha II
21.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, a HUGE re-match is going down with Mantz v Rocha. That's right, the most watched episode of the Schmoedown will get another go as The Outlaw John Rocha takes on Scott "Movie" Mantz with the winner entering the Ultimate Schmoedown Tournament for a chance to run the table and take a shot at the belt.

22.title: Josh Macuga Vs JTE
22.plot: It's time for The Movie Trivia Schmoedown. This week, a HUGE match-up to see who will enter the Ultimate Schmoedown Tournament. JTE takes on The Wildman Josh Macuga, winner advances, loser, walks away with their head between their legs.

0.title: 2017 Movie Trivia Schmoedown Awards
0.plot: Join us as we celebrate the last year of Movie Trivia Schmoedown matches, competitors and fans with the 2017 Schmoedown Awards. Hosted by Mark "Baby Carrots" Ellis, watch as your favorite competitors present awards for the greatest competitors, biggest comeback performance, best entrance, favorite celebrity match, favorite podcast/aftershow and more.

1.title: Mike Kalinowski Vs. JTE Vs. Rachel Cushing
1.plot: In this season opener, the top three singles league competitors enter a triple threat match to determine who will vie for the championship belt against Samm Levine. "Little Evil" JTE faces off against Rachel "The Crusher" Cushing and Mike "KO" Kalinowski.

2.title: Top That Vs. Top 10
2.plot: It's time for the Movie Trivia Schmoedown, the game show that makes a sport out of movie knowledge. In this team league match, Team Top 10, fresh off their revenge victory against Team Action, takes on the team of Jim Vejvoda and Eric Goldman of Team Top That in a #1 Contenders Match.

4.title: Innergeekdom Fatal Five Way
4.plot: On this week's episode of the Movie Trivia Schmoedown, the Innergeekdom Division returns in 2018 in a BIG way with a 5 Way Match. Four new competitors and one old favorite battle to see who might emerge as a possible future contender for the Inner Geekdom Championship. 'The Enforcer' Mark Donica, 'The Answer Man' Mike Carlson, 'Crazy' Coy Jandreau, 'Haymaker' Adam Hlavac and Keetin 'Magic' Marchi go head to head in three rounds of exciting Schmoedown action.

5.title: Ash Vs. The Evil Dead
5.plot: On this week's episode of the Celebrity Movie Trivia Schmoedown, Ray Santiago and Dana DeLorenzo from 'Ash vs Evil Dead' join Collider Heroes' Jon Schnepp and Critically Acclaimed's Witney Seibold to battle it out for Movie Trivia supremacy on the show. The King himself Bruce Capmbell joins the commentary team of Mark Ellis and Mark Reilly to call this match. It's our first Celebrity Schmoedown of 2018 and its GROOVY. See how you do against these very knowledgeable competitors and if you'll be saying Hail to the King or Queen when it's all over.

1.title: Dan Murrell Vs Ethan Erwin II/Ellison vs The Machine: Live From New York!
1.plot: Recorded live from the Roulette Theater in Brooklyn, it's the season six premiere of the Movie Trivia Schmoedown. Ethan 'Big Time' Erwin puts his new title on the line against #1 contender and former champion 'Dangerous' Dan Murrell. Plus, the night begins with two fearsome competitors duking it out: Jeannine the Machine VS 'The Cobra' Chance Ellison.

imdb.plot outline: Movie Trivia Schmoedown is your weekly WWE style Movie Trivia Competition where industry professionals from around the Galaxy battle head to head in the ultimate test of movie knowledge. Hosted by Kristian Harloff and Mark Ellis, each competitor climbs the rankings in search of their ultimate prize - the Movie Trivia Schmoedown championship belt. Movie Trivia Schmoedown drops every Tuesday and Friday afternoon.
